Based on study resources, we decided that each household would be offered the option of purchasing up to two stoves consisting of any combination of the higher and/or lower quality stove models at prices randomly assigned to that household’s cluster. Therefore, each choice set consisted of 6 alternatives (1–2 stoves of only one model, 1 of each model, or no stoves), and the only components of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
